"return \"the <literal>\\0</literal> (NUL) character\" (not the same as the "
"number zero ASCII)"
msgstr ""
"\"<literal>\\0</literal> (NUL) 文字\" を返す (ASCII の数字のゼロとは違う)"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><table><tgroup><tbody><row><entry>
