"Manual (PDF)</ulink> で説明されています。"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><tip><para>
msgid ""
"Running other GNU/Linux distributions such as <ulink url=\"&ubuntu;"
"\">Ubuntu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"&fedra;\">Fedra</ulink> under <ulink url="
"\"&virtualization;\">virtualization</ulink> is a great way to learn "
"configuration tips.  Other proprietary OSs may be run nicely under this GNU/"
"Linux <ulink url=\"&virtualization;\">virtualization</ulink>, too."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"&ubuntu;\">Ubuntu</ulink> や <ulink url=\"&fedra;\">Fedra</"
