msgid ""
"One of following procedures extract differences between two source files and "
"create unified diff files \"<literal>file.patch0</literal>\" or "
"\"<literal>file.patch1</literal>\" depending on the file location."
msgstr ""
"ファイルの場所次第で次の手順のひとつに従うとふたつのソースファイル間の相違を"
